org.oboparser.obo

Class OBOTerm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.oboparser.obo.OBOStanza
      • org.oboparser.obo.OBOTerm

  • public class OBOTerm
extends OBOStanza
    OBOTerm represent an OBO stanza that begins with the "[Term]" string. Each term must have (at a minimum) a "name" field.
    Author:
    Timothy Danford
